{"tid":732073,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"萊因克爾批麥巴比假摔：無法想像他是從哪兒學了這一套","createTime":"2018-07-06T16:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T17:03:58.000Z","uid":8985,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40b963d3b42ad54158a02094b43388f112fc9d44","tid":732073,"uid":8985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"在剛剛結束的法國和烏拉圭的世界盃四分之一決賽中，麥巴比在進攻中的一次摔倒險些引發了兩隊球員的衝突。對於麥巴比的這次摔倒，萊因克爾也進行了一番評論。<br />\n<br />\n萊因克爾說：&ldquo;我的天啊，我無法想像他是從哪兒學了這一套。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n萊因克爾這番話似乎有含沙射影之嫌，這也引起了一名巴西記者的不滿，這名巴西記者回復萊因克爾：&ldquo;英格蘭和哥倫比亞的比賽簡直是恥辱，你們英格蘭隊員都假摔了多少次！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n萊因克爾隨後回復到：&ldquo;你的戲跟某些球員一樣多，你開心就好。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"d0978919af771ccd65bbfe82a1dcd6fd0a552750","tid":732073,"uid":68916,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"會教佢插水嘅,除咗哈姆太郎仲有邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b45aa66cc374a614be2a474efa623f55c9a62f","tid":732073,"uid":187076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/005653_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F005653_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=659b364b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d6ea3232c49b63bed47ca16bef3760d92974025","tid":732073,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"你開心就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00507cd6a300df40cb48ff375193b23fc905d6c","tid":732073,"uid":156527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"估唔到隻忍者龜學野幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab5e1c090b6c24129d5cc32b58be47fdd268d22","tid":732073,"uid":41309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"你的戲跟某些球員一樣多，你開心就好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}